{"tid":2277221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「無罩」白宮幕僚長確診","createTime":"2020-11-08T10:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T10:11:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4b18e9294ff79c4c34ca02ebfb70bc49e46ff7","tid":2277221,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/RHDLMQS5LFGZFL7KH2FPJF24YU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FRHDLMQS5LFGZFL7KH2FPJF24YU%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7woLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=1dfd0ca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FRHDLMQS5LFGZFL7KH2FPJF24YU%2F&h=bafc2530\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/RHDLMQS5LFGZFL7KH2FPJF24YU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「無罩」白宮幕僚長確診<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RPDuPy2hatIAcLiaswIG8gL37JY=/898x581/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/64WZHYO5ERCG3LZC45OF52YT3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRPDuPy2hatIAcLiaswIG8gL37JY%3D%2F898x581%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F64WZHYO5ERCG3LZC45OF52YT3I.jpg&h=342ad498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梅多斯上周一曾隨特朗普出席造勢活動，其間沒戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮幕僚長梅多斯（Mark Meadows）確診武漢肺炎，同期確診還有特朗普的競選助理特雷納（Nick Trainer）。兩名高級政府官員證實消息，透露還有數名白宮員工確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一選舉法官疑染疫亡<br />\n<br />\n據報61歲的梅多斯上周三對病毒檢測呈陽性。當日是他最後一次現身。。。。。。。。。。。競選期間他多次跟隨特朗普出席造勢活動，往往不戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n另外，密蘇里州一名選舉法官感染武漢肺炎後死亡，當。。。。。。。。。。。據了解其家人不知她染疫，只有她伴侶知道。<br />\n<br />\n該名法官上月30日確診武肺，但未有理會隔離指引，。。。。。。。。。，呼籲其他選舉法官接受病毒檢測。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"}]}